Subject: [PATCH] Exclude recovery as A/B OTA partition

As I use a special version of the Lineage recovery for the hardened build,
I would like to avoid, that the recovery always gets overwritten, when
flashing LineageOS.

Credits to: stay steadfast <steadfasterX@users.noreply.github.com>

Change-Id: I8d4a6435576b3a1503e455bd696720ac1bb700aa
---
 BoardConfig.mk | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/BoardConfig.mk b/BoardConfig.mk
index f890173..4d03394 100644
--- a/BoardConfig.mk
+++ b/BoardConfig.mk
@@ -13,7 +13,6 @@ DEVICE_PATH := device/oneplus/hotdog
 AB_OTA_PARTITIONS += \
     odm \
     product \
-    recovery \
     system_ext \
     vbmeta_system
 
